{"word":"H645 - אֵפֹו - ʼêphôw - ay-fo' - Here","slug":"H645","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אֵפֹו</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼêphôw"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ay-fo'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Here"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D0;&#x05E4;&#x05D5;&#x05D0;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D0;&#x05E4;&#x05D5; - 'e&#x0302;pho&#x0302;  'e&#x0302;pho&#x0302;'</b> - <i>ay-fo', ay-fo'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H6311\">H6311</a>; strictly a demonstrative particle, <i>here</i>; but used of time, <i>now</i> or <i>then: - </i>here, now, where?"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H647\">H647</a>"}]}